    <div class="bb-content">
        <div>
            <h5 class="text-primary">THE ISSUE</h5>
                            <div class="bb-body">
                    Up to 270.5 million&nbsp;people are estimated to be acutely food insecure or at high risk across 80 countries (2021).
                </div>
                                            </div>
    </div>
</div>


    <div id="shadow-divide-container" class="spacer_desktop_10 spacer_tablet_10 spacer_mobile_10">
